sage.from.last_name }} !\n\nPour recevoir les notifications et messages personnalisés, vous devez enregistrer vos informations :\n\n• 🔢 Code X3\n• 🌍 Langue préférée\n\nCliquez sur le bouton ci-dessous pour commencer :","replyMarkup":"inlineKeyboard","inlineKeyboard":{"rows":[{"row":{"buttons":[{"text":"▶️ Commencer","additionalFields":{"callback_data":"=start_registration"}}]}}]},"additionalFields":{"appendAttribution":false}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.telegram","typeVersion":1.2,"position":[720,-400],"id":"c983738f-7d52-4d63-bc6d-1fa696cd3901","name":"Message Bienvenue Nouveau","webhookId":"93f337d7-96a9-43a7-8ff2-817a8551e781","credentials":{"telegramApi":{"id":"45w69gDsqGFcxPpu","name":"Notification"}}},{"parameters":{"resource":"callback","queryId":"={{ $json.callback_query.id }}","additionalFields":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.telegram","typeVersion":1.2,"position":[48,-304],"id":"63164279-3e1e-47c4-98d7-cfea026fea12","name":"Answer Callback Query","webhookId":"718de440-6734-456c-a3d7-8dbce9ad0ed4","credentials":{"telegramApi":{"id":"45w69gDsqGFcxPpu","name":"Notification"}}},{"parameters":{"chatId":"={{ $('Telegram Trigger1').item.json.callback_query.from.id }}","text":"🔢 **Étape 1/2 : Code salarié**  \n\nVeuillez saisir votre code X3 (format : S suivi de 4 chiffres)  \n📝 **Exemple :** S1234  \n\n👉 Tapez votre code ci-dessous :","replyMarkup":"forceReply","forceReply":{"force_reply":false},"additionalFields":{"appendAttribution":false}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.telegram","typeVersion":1.2,"position":[272,-304],"id":"59039875-6e8a-49a6-b098-7aece18dff64","name":"Demander Code X3","webhookId":"8db1912e-1197-443b-aa9d-c56298cd9792","credentials":{"telegramApi":{"id":"45w69gDsqGFcxPpu","name":"Notification"}}},{"parameters":{"updates":["message","callback_query"],"additionalFields":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.telegramTrigger","typeVersion":1.2,"position":[-400,80],"id":"cf3634e3-0119-47d0-b319-346768c7d918","name":"Telegram Trigger1","webhookId":"8b7071df-01c2-469a-b9ab-22bbb39721fa","credentials":{"telegramApi":{"id":"45w69gDsqGFcxPpu","name":"Notification"}}},{"parameters":{"operation":"executeQuery","query":"SELECT \n    '{{ $json.message.chat.id }}' AS CHAT_ID,\n\n    CASE \n        -- ENREGISTRÉ_COMPLET : Code X3 + Langue réelle\n        WHEN EXISTS (\n            SELECT 1\n            FROM jbelrh.JBELRH.YAIINFOSAL\n            WHERE TIDCHAT_0 = '{{ $json.message.chat.id }}'\n              AND XSAL_0 IS NOT NULL\n              AND TRIM(LAN_0) <> ''\n        )\n        THEN 'ENREGISTRÉ_COMPLET'\n\n        -- EN_ATTENTE_LANGUE : Code X3 ok mais langue vide ou null\n        WHEN EXISTS (\n            SELECT 1\n            FROM jbelrh.JBELRH.YAIINFOSAL\n            WHERE TIDCHAT_0 = '{{ $json.message.chat.id }}'\n              AND XSAL_0 IS NOT NULL\n              AND (LAN_0 IS NULL OR TRIM(LAN_0) = '')\n        )\n        THEN 'EN_ATTENTE_LANGUE'\n\n        -- NOUVEAU\n        ELSE 'NOUVEAU'\n    END AS ETAT_UTILISATEUR,\n\n    MAX(t.XSAL_0)      AS Code_X3,\n    NULLIF(TRIM(MAX(t.LAN_0)), '') AS Langue,\n    MAX(t.CREDATTIM_0) AS Date_creation\n\nFROM jbelrh.JBELRH.YAIINFOSAL t\nWHERE t.TIDCHAT_0 = '{{ $json.message.chat.id }}';\n"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.microsoftSql","typeVersion":1.1,"position":[48,-592],"id":"83650df8-89a5-44c3-b742-3fa343d8fc86","name":"Microsoft SQL","credentials":{"microsoftSql":{"id":"urE2RXcTk330zGDx","name":"sageRH"}}},{"parameters":{"operation":"executeQuery","query":"DECLARE @CODE_VERIF VARCHAR(6);\n\n-- Génération d’un code à 6 chiffres\nSET @CODE_VERIF = RIGHT(\n    '000000' + CAST(ABS(CHECKSUM(NEWID())) % 1000000 AS VARCHAR),\n    6\n);\n\nSELECT\n    '{{ $json.CODE_ENVOYE }}' AS code_x3,\n    t.XNAMSAL_0 AS nom,\n    t.XPRENOM_0 AS prenom,\n    t.XEMAIL_0 AS email,\n    CASE\n        WHEN t.XSAL_0 IS NOT NULL THEN 'OUI'\n        ELSE 'NON'\n    END AS EXISTE,\n    CASE\n        WHEN t.XSAL_0 IS NOT NULL THEN 'CODE_ENVOYE'\n        ELSE 'ERREUR'\n    END AS ETAT_VERIFICATION,\n    @CODE_VERIF AS CODE_A_ENVOYER -- 👉 à envoyer par email\nFROM jbelrh.JBELRH.XSAL t\nWHERE t.XSAL_0 = '{{ $json.CODE_ENVOYE }}';\n"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.microsoftSql","typeVersion":1.1,"position":[496,-208],"id":"4a57f745-371f-4ad1-9e19-a169b823055f","name":"Microsoft SQL1","credentials":{"microsoftSql":{"id":"2sA9ZAsYgvC4gdIr","name":"X3BI"}}},{"parameters":{"chatId":"={{ $node['Telegram Trigger1'].json.message.chat.id }}","text":"❌ **Code non reconnu**\n\nLe code que vous avez saisi ne correspond à aucun salarié dans notre système.\n\n🔍 **Vérifications :**\n   • Le format est-il correct ? (S + 4 chiffres)\n   • Avez-vous bien tapé tous les caractères ?\n\n📝 **Exemple de code valide :** S1234\n\n🔄 Veuillez réessayer en saisissant un code valide.\n\n💬 En cas de problème, contactez le service RH.","additionalFields":{"appendAttribution":false}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.telegram","typeVersion":1.2,"position":[944,80],"id":"a1380864-e9e8-4ec5-ae68-20b9b23bc710","name":"Send a text message","webhookId":"b05971f1-82b8-4798-9b67-e13121156b32","credentials":{"telegramApi":{"id":"45w69gDsqGFcxPpu","name":"Notification"}}},{"parameters":{"chatId":"={{ $node['Telegram Trigger1'].json.message.chat.id }}","text":"✅ **Code validé avec succès !**\n\n🌍 **Étape 2/2 : Langue de communication**\n\nDans quelle langue souhaitez-vous recevoir vos notifications ?\n\n👇 Choisissez votre langue préférée :","replyMarkup":"inlineKeyboard","inlineKeyboard":{"rows":[{"row":{"buttons":[{"text":"🇫🇷 Français","additionalFields":{"callback_data":"=lang_FRA_{{ $('If').item.json.code_x3 }}"}},{"text":"🇬🇧 English","additionalFields":{"callback_data":"=lang_ENG_{{ $('If').item.json.code_x3 }}"}}]}},{"row":{"buttons":[{"text":"🇪🇸 Español","additionalFields":{"callback_data":"=lang_ESP_{{ $('If').item.json.code_x3 }}"}},{"text":"🇸🇦 العربية","additionalFields":{"callback_data":"=lang_ARA_{{ $('If').item.json.code_x3 }}"}}]}}]},"additionalFields":{"appendAttribution":false}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.telegram","typeVersion":1.2,"position":[944,272],"id":"97ec030f-3c9c-4611-8e47-899db10771a7","name":"Demander Langue","webhookId":"ba13702c-f10e-40d4-865b-07c7c370762e","credentials":{"telegramApi":{"id":"45w69gDsqGFcxPpu","name":"Notification"}}},{"parameters":{"jsCode":"// Récupération des données du callback\nconst callbackData = $json.callback_query.data;\nconst chatId = $json.callback_query.from.id;\n\n// Regex pour matcher: lang_XXX_SXXXX\nconst regex = /^lang_(FRA|ENG|ARA|ESP)_([Ss][0-9]{4})$/;\n\nif (!regex.test(callbackData)) {\n  return [{\n    json: {\n      valid: false,\n      message: 'Format invalide',\n      callback_data: callbackData\n    }\n  }];\n}\n\n// Extraction langue et code\nconst match = callbackData.match(regex);\nconst langueCode = match[1]; // FRA, ENG, ARA, ESP\nconst codeX3 = match[2];     // S1499\n\n// Mapping des langues\nconst languages = {\n  FRA: 'Français',\n  ENG: 'English',\n  ARA: 'العربية',\n  ESP: 'Español'\n};\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    valid: true,\n    langue_code: langueCode,\n    langue_nom: languages[langueCode],\n    code_x3: codeX3,\n    chat_id: chatId\n  }\n}];"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[48,272],"id":"53c7a26d-232e-4645-be4b-c4d4f9569ab0","name":"Code"},{"parameters":{"chatId":"={{ $('Telegram Trigger1').item.json.callback_query.from.id }}","text":"🎉 **Inscription réussie !**\n\nFélicitations, votre profil est maintenant complet et actif.\n\n✅ **Configuration enregistrée :**\n   • Code X3 : Validé\n   • Langue : Configurée\n\n📬 Vous recevrez désormais toutes les notifications personnalisées dans votre langue.\n\nMerci et bienvenue ! 👋","additionalFields":{"appendAttribution":false}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.telegram","typeVersion":1.2,"position":[496,272],"id":"c4581ad4-6a4a-40ae-afc0-ad9ce5a5d083","name":"Send a text message1","webhookId":"bd6c640b-60ea-4d58-b9f5-dc53f38c4043","credentials":{"telegramApi":{"id":"45w69gDsqGFcxPpu","name":"Notification"}}},{"parameters":{"method":"PUT","url":"=http://192.168